  "summary": "Match, build, and explore! Travel the world and solve puzzles along the way!",
  "description": "Welcome to Matching Go, a thrilling match-3 puzzle game where you explore the world alongside Chloe and her adorable corgi Ollie! Whether you’re a casual player or a puzzle expert, Matching Go offers endless fun and a delightful journey. Get ready to match, collect, and build as you travel to breathtaking destinations!\n\nJoin Chloe and Ollie on their adventure across the globe! Start your match-3 journey now and see where the next puzzle takes you!\n\nFEATURES OF MATCHING GO:\n\n🎮 Engaging Puzzle Gameplay\n‒ Match 3 or more colorful objects to unleash exciting combos and power-ups!\n‒ Levels designed for players of all skill levels, from easy to challenging!\n\n🌍 Travel the World \n‒ Discover iconic cities like New York, London, and Paris, alongside imaginative realms like Christmas Village, Fairyland and so on!\n‒ Build exquisite landmarks as you pass new levels and gather mallets!\n\n✨ Stunning Visuals\n‒ Every map comes to life with vibrant colors and fabulous designs!\n‒ Enjoy the thrill of matching as explosive animations and unique effects make every game more satisfying!\n\n🎁 Special Rewards \n‒ Earn daily bonuses and participate in exciting events to win prizes!\n‒ Speed up with various winning streak boosters!\n\n⚔️ Compete with Others\n‒ Challenge other players on the leaderboard!\n‒ Climb the ranks and prove your puzzle-solving skills to become the top player!\n\nAre you ready to embark on a world of fun and puzzles?  Download Matching Go now and start your trip!🚀\n\nGot questions or feedback? Reach us at blockpuzzleonlinestudio@gmail.com. We're always here to help!",
  "recentChanges": "Set off on a thrilling journey in Matching Go! New content is here—join us on an exciting world journey!<br>‒ Improved overall performance and fixed known bugs.<br>Get ready for new adventures! Every 1-2 weeks, we&#39;re adding 100 exciting new levels and fresh destinations to explore!",
  "developerWebsite": "https://www.dingshanmobile.com/",
  "developerEmail": "blockpuzzleonlinestudio@gmail.com",
